All hail the one and true mongod.

install mongo
`brew install mongo`

make directory for mongo to store data
`sudo mkdir -p /data/db`

`whoami`
this should return whatever name you gave yourself when you set up your operating system

`sudo chown -Rv yourname /data/db`

`mongod`
this should successfully start the mongo server
